<h1>Contact Us!</h1>
<br></br>
<div class="row-fluid">
<div class="span4">
<%= simple_form_for ContactForm.new, url: {action: "create"} do |f| %>
	<%= f.label :Name %><%= f.text_field :name %><br />
	<%= f.label :Email %><%= f.text_field :email %><br />
	<%= f.label :Subject %><%= f.select :inquiry, options_for_select(["Performance", "Sponsorship", "Involvement", "Other"])%><br />
	<%= f.label :Message %><%= f.text_area :message, :cols => "30", :rows => "10" %><br />
    <%= f.submit "Submit"%>
<% end %>
</div>
<div class="span8">
<img alt="Raas Friends and Family" src="/assets/raas_ff.jpg">
<p>
Besides competing across the nation, Basmati Raas performs at various on-campus and off-campus events such as weddings, company events, and other occasions. <br> 
Most recently, the team was the opening act for Ted-Ex Stanford, and was one of the selected student groups for the Bing Concert Hall Student Showcase. <br>
</p>

<p>As a student group, we receive limited funding from the university which is not enough to cover the yearly expenses associated with performing, such as costumes, props, backdrops, travel, and lodging. <br>
Due to the large number of people that we come into contact with throughout the year, we believe that our organization is a great vehicle for a business to reach prospective customers. Please contact us if you are interested in suppporting Basmati Raas, and/or showcasing your organization!</p>

<p> Other Questions? Please enter your information into the form to the left, and our captains will be in touch as soon as possible.</p>
</div>

</div>